and assistance and small grants?

00:56:47.360 --> 00:56:53.670 position:56%
But we also need to make sure that
we provide a system that it monitors

00:56:53.670 --> 00:56:58.150
and provides -- establishes
transparency and accountability

00:56:58.150 --> 00:57:01.430
of these grassroots
organizations that are emerging

00:57:01.430 --> 00:57:03.900
to provide services
in their communities.

00:57:03.900 --> 00:57:09.200
Now let me conclude my
remarks by saying that we

00:57:09.200 --> 00:57:11.480
as Afghan women are very
pleased that the window

00:57:11.480 --> 00:57:15.890
of opportunity has opened
for us, and we have hope,

00:57:15.890 --> 00:57:19.910
but we need to make sure that the
Afghan people are given a voice

00:57:19.910 --> 00:57:24.610
and they are empowered because
I think that the best solution

00:57:24.610 --> 00:57:30.740
to bring to the war on terrorism
and to waging war on intolerance

00:57:30.740 --> 00:57:33.210
in Afghanistan lies
within the Afghan people,

00:57:33.210 --> 00:57:37.150
and the Afghan people
are very tolerant minded

00:57:37.150 --> 00:57:39.070
and civil society minded.

00:57:39.070 --> 00:57:41.760
